        "~~~\n",
        "\n",
        "Then select the environment created by uv as this notebook's kernel.\n",
        "\n",
        "Required accounts:\n",
        "\n",
        "- Vercel AI Gateway for generation, embeddings, the RAG answer model, and judges\n",
        "- LangSmith for the dataset and experiments\n",
