      "source": [
        "#### Question #5\n",
        "\n",
        "Give one example where answer correctness and groundedness could disagree. What\n",
        "would that disagreement tell you to inspect in the trace?\n",
        "\n",
        "##### Answer\n",
        "\n",
        "A good example is when the RAG system produces a correct answer for the wrong reason.\n",
        "\n",
        "Here is an example:\n",
        "\n",
        "Question: How often should cats receive rabies vaccinations?\n",
        "Answer: Cats should receive annual rabies vaccinations\n",
        "\n",
        "Retrieved Contexts (Wrong): No rabies information was retrieved.\n",
